{"tid":2290504,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"安歷基：德國拿出了最強陣容，西班牙還有人沒入選","createTime":"2020-11-18T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T17:24:58.000Z","uid":38189,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f395fdee2999fc64ea8a884041a0b989290791db","tid":2290504,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"對於這場比賽您是怎麼看的，您覺得德國的表現在您的預期之中嗎？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得德國是有備而來的，他們拿出了最強的陣容，除去基米希，剩下都是最強的球員。 我們開場的逼搶不錯，迫使德國隊不得不進行長傳，這也是他們最不舒服的打法。 在進攻上我們沒有失誤，這也是我執教國家隊以來最完美的比賽。<br />\n<br />\n 最好的是今天我們沒有錯失機會，當你比對手錶現，創造更多的機會，卻就是不進球，就像之前的比賽那樣。 這是第一次西班牙進入歐國聯的四角賽，這對我們來說是一個很棒的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n串到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫疤報仇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e62fef49a704a3ab81be38b49c4dd5b920ad6c","tid":2290504,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca869e2860a9066b8f16194a5776ac2c04dbfa57","tid":2290504,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:05:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb72f8cf0eb1fd4278a6ac06a1db84b2a270125e","tid":2290504,"uid":308020,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:06:30.000Z","msg":"德國都未full team啦，你見到有保定梅拿Hummels咩"},{"pid":"6453e821fea5e1fdb0ea1d7b221a088966248864","tid":2290504,"uid":117802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:06:38.000Z","msg":"有奧燒贏7-6"},{"pid":"c6f4838e27455a76860329d68fda8269cd968cdc","tid":2290504,"uid":311626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T05:06:42.000Z","msg":"等樓主料，結果冇出 冇買德國，樓主料堅"},{"pid":"5b7490a33eb34862bac577d137c92090ace9663e","tid":2290504,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6